WEBVTT

00:00:40.280 --> 00:00:41.159
Love me.

00:00:42.399 --> 00:00:43.560
Thank you, Dahai.

00:00:44.280 --> 00:00:46.079
Only you wouldn't despise me.

00:00:47.759 --> 00:00:48.479
No way.

00:00:48.920 --> 00:00:49.719
She's my mother.

00:00:50.799 --> 00:00:51.679
Zhu Yihai.

00:00:52.359 --> 00:00:53.600
Is that Huilian's necklace?

00:00:53.960 --> 00:00:56.079
I'll take everyone close to you

00:00:56.640 --> 00:01:00.560
and finish them off one by one.

00:01:00.799 --> 00:01:01.799
Do I even have a choice?

00:01:01.799 --> 00:01:02.840
You don't.

00:01:06.920 --> 00:01:07.920
Zhu Yihai.

00:01:08.079 --> 00:01:10.920
How did you stir up such a huge mess back then?

00:01:16.640 --> 00:01:17.200
Hold on.

00:01:17.439 --> 00:01:20.159
If Qian Huilian really is my mother,

00:01:20.480 --> 00:01:21.079
then that means

00:01:21.079 --> 00:01:22.560
back then, you rescued her

00:01:22.560 --> 00:01:23.840
right out of Long Xiao's hands.

00:01:24.480 --> 00:01:25.280
You old bastard.

00:01:25.560 --> 00:01:28.079
Tell me how the hell you pulled it off.

00:01:29.879 --> 00:01:31.560
You guys, you guys...

00:01:33.879 --> 00:01:35.159
What are you all doing here?

00:01:35.359 --> 00:01:36.239
With all this commotion,

00:01:36.239 --> 00:01:38.519
how could we not come, you big idiot?

00:01:38.640 --> 00:01:39.439
Dali.

00:01:40.480 --> 00:01:41.280
Erhu.

00:01:41.760 --> 00:01:42.560
Zhu Yihai.

00:01:42.920 --> 00:01:45.680
Dongxing also has beef with Long Xiao.

00:01:46.319 --> 00:01:48.000
Old grudges and new, we'll settle them together.

00:01:49.120 --> 00:01:50.359
Ge Bing, you...

00:01:50.359 --> 00:01:52.280
Long Xiao's after my dad's factory.

00:01:52.359 --> 00:01:54.879
Chief Dao and I can't just stand by.

00:01:58.760 --> 00:01:59.560
Let's take him down.

00:02:01.799 --> 00:02:02.599
Thanks.

00:02:02.799 --> 00:02:03.159
All right.

00:02:03.159 --> 00:02:04.079
Quit dragging your feet.

00:02:04.079 --> 00:02:04.760
You're the smart one.

00:02:04.760 --> 00:02:05.920
Tell us what to do already.

00:02:06.480 --> 00:02:07.640
Jiao Jing, you tell them.

00:02:07.640 --> 00:02:08.719
What's Long Xiao planning?

00:02:09.719 --> 00:02:11.479
It's not just the Aimin Street contract.

00:02:12.120 --> 00:02:13.960
Everyone here is his target.

00:02:14.360 --> 00:02:15.319
So I think,

00:02:15.719 --> 00:02:16.479
while Zhu Yihai and I

00:02:16.479 --> 00:02:18.400
go to Dream Lover to find Qian Huilian,

00:02:18.719 --> 00:02:19.840
the rest of you should split up

00:02:20.159 --> 00:02:21.080
and keep yourselves safe.

00:02:21.360 --> 00:02:22.879
Why don't we stick together?

00:02:24.319 --> 00:02:25.800
You wanna get wiped out in one swoop?

00:02:27.879 --> 00:02:28.800
You old geezer.

00:02:29.960 --> 00:02:32.159
That's how you handled Long Xiao back then, right?

00:02:33.599 --> 00:02:35.159
Whatever you could solve,

00:02:36.560 --> 00:02:37.680
I sure as hell can too.

00:02:39.120 --> 00:02:40.240
This leather jacket looks pretty sharp.

00:02:40.400 --> 00:02:41.199
Mind if I borrow it?

00:02:42.080 --> 00:02:43.240
I've got a tough fight ahead.

00:02:55.319 --> 00:02:57.120
I saw Qian Huilian here yesterday.

00:02:58.000 --> 00:02:58.800
Alright.

00:02:59.159 --> 00:03:00.680
Find a way to rescue Huilian.

00:03:00.840 --> 00:03:01.919
I'll distract them.

00:03:02.439 --> 00:03:03.759
You'll distract them?

00:03:05.080 --> 00:03:06.000
Can you handle it?

00:03:06.960 --> 00:03:07.919
Don't worry about it.

00:03:14.520 --> 00:03:16.639
Hey everyone, look over here!

00:03:17.280 --> 00:03:19.439
New Year's Day is almost here.

00:03:19.439 --> 00:03:23.639
I, Zhu Yihai, will perform a special act.

00:03:23.639 --> 00:03:25.120
You've all seen Errenzhuan, right?

00:03:26.000 --> 00:03:28.080
I'll do an Errenzhuan number.

00:03:31.240 --> 00:03:31.759
Dali.

00:03:34.240 --> 00:03:35.800
How's Weiwei? Has she woken up?

00:03:36.560 --> 00:03:37.560
Not yet.

00:03:37.560 --> 00:03:38.759
But thank you.

00:03:38.759 --> 00:03:41.360
for finding emergency plasma in the city.

00:03:41.599 --> 00:03:42.719
I really didn't do much.

00:03:42.719 --> 00:03:44.000
My dad arranged all of it.

00:03:46.240 --> 00:03:48.240
With him like this, I can't leave.

00:03:48.240 --> 00:03:49.719
You should hurry back to the warehouse.

00:03:49.719 --> 00:03:50.680
It's safer over there.

00:03:52.479 --> 00:03:54.960
I wonder how things are at the warehouse.

00:03:55.800 --> 00:03:56.360
Oh my.

00:03:56.639 --> 00:03:59.199
Isn't this our factory's old warehouse?

00:03:59.879 --> 00:04:01.479
Zhu Yihai really knows how to pick spots.

00:04:02.960 --> 00:04:03.520
Lili.

00:04:04.120 --> 00:04:04.960
You know what?

00:04:05.360 --> 00:04:06.560
Our Huilian,

00:04:06.560 --> 00:04:07.479
right here in this very place,

00:04:07.479 --> 00:04:09.159
swore brotherhood with Zhu Yihai's crew.

00:04:09.479 --> 00:04:12.360
Each got a necklace engraved with "Yi."

00:04:12.719 --> 00:04:14.159
Acting like it was the real deal.

00:04:15.240 --> 00:04:16.040
Do you have one?

00:04:16.720 --> 00:04:17.519
No, I don't.

00:04:23.680 --> 00:04:24.759
Dao Balian.

00:04:25.639 --> 00:04:27.040
Let me ask you a question.

00:04:27.920 --> 00:04:28.720
Go ahead.

00:04:30.079 --> 00:04:32.399
If the person you love pushed you away,

00:04:34.519 --> 00:04:35.480
what would you do?

00:04:39.319 --> 00:04:40.120
What are you doing?

00:04:40.680 --> 00:04:41.240
Look.

00:04:41.600 --> 00:04:43.120
Didn't you push me away too?

00:04:43.560 --> 00:04:44.800
But you didn't leave.

00:04:44.800 --> 00:04:45.800
You're still hanging around here.

00:04:45.800 --> 00:04:47.399
Watching from afar is good enough.

00:04:51.279 --> 00:04:52.680
I wonder when Zhu Yihai

00:04:52.920 --> 00:04:54.800
will manage to find our Huilian.

00:05:00.920 --> 00:05:03.600
The young pay New Year respects to the old,

00:05:04.480 --> 00:05:06.160
no need to ask about

00:05:06.160 --> 00:05:07.959
who's a man and who's a woman.

00:05:16.680 --> 00:05:17.680
Yihai.

00:05:18.600 --> 00:05:19.160
Really

00:05:19.560 --> 00:05:21.199
You surprise me every single time

00:05:21.600 --> 00:05:22.920
You've got quite a few tricks up your sleeve

00:05:23.439 --> 00:05:24.959
You showed up before I finished singing

00:05:26.439 --> 00:05:26.959
Long Xiao.

00:05:26.959 --> 00:05:27.600
Guess I'm just early

00:05:28.399 --> 00:05:30.519
I came here today to negotiate terms

00:05:30.519 --> 00:05:31.319
What's up?

00:05:31.879 --> 00:05:33.399
Had a sudden change of heart?

00:05:33.399 --> 00:05:34.800
You've got a huge empire

00:05:34.800 --> 00:05:37.199
I run a pool hall, how could I fight you?

00:05:37.720 --> 00:05:39.639
Here's the deal, you let Huilian go

00:05:40.040 --> 00:05:42.560
and take a smaller cut of Aimin Street.

00:05:42.560 --> 00:05:44.720
Weren't you the one who insisted

00:05:45.040 --> 00:05:47.000
that fifty-two percent was your lifeline?

00:05:47.279 --> 00:05:49.839
How did your lifeline suddenly change?

00:05:50.399 --> 00:05:51.800
Forget fifty-two

00:05:52.439 --> 00:05:53.600
Fifty-one

00:05:56.160 --> 00:05:57.560
Zhu Yihai, oh Zhu Yihai

00:05:59.120 --> 00:06:00.759
You're actually quite the talent

00:06:01.959 --> 00:06:03.079
What a shame

00:06:03.399 --> 00:06:04.560
Too much?

00:06:04.759 --> 00:06:06.079
Forty-nine, how about that?

00:06:06.759 --> 00:06:08.519
How long are you gonna keep yapping?

00:06:09.360 --> 00:06:10.000
No, hold on

00:06:10.240 --> 00:06:11.720
You told me you're a businessman

00:06:11.720 --> 00:06:13.319
So I'm just talking business with you

00:06:13.800 --> 00:06:14.600
Zhu Yihai

00:06:15.839 --> 00:06:17.959
Quit playing your little games with me

00:06:19.160 --> 00:06:20.240
Are you waiting

00:06:21.040 --> 00:06:21.800
for her?

00:06:27.120 --> 00:06:28.279
Jiao Jing

00:06:32.759 --> 00:06:33.560
Zhu Yihai

00:06:34.560 --> 00:06:36.279
You walked right into the trap after all

00:06:37.120 --> 00:06:37.680
Lili

00:06:38.399 --> 00:06:40.920
Think Zhu Yihai's plan will work?

00:06:41.639 --> 00:06:43.439
Something feels off to me

00:06:46.000 --> 00:06:47.240
You're lying to me again, aren't you?

00:06:47.639 --> 00:06:49.199
That's on you for being weak.

00:06:49.759 --> 00:06:53.199
Falling for the same woman twice

00:06:57.120 --> 00:06:58.680
I suggest you let Huilian go

00:06:58.680 --> 00:07:00.360
Or else I'll burn this agreement

00:07:00.600 --> 00:07:01.399
Burn it

00:07:01.879 --> 00:07:03.240
Go ahead, burn it

00:07:03.399 --> 00:07:04.600
Come on, hurry up and burn it

00:07:05.399 --> 00:07:06.199
Have you noticed

00:07:06.199 --> 00:07:08.160
you've misunderstood one thing all along?

00:07:08.519 --> 00:07:10.000
Think about Long Xiao

00:07:10.000 --> 00:07:11.160
If he wanted Aimin Street

00:07:11.160 --> 00:07:12.519
why insist on going through Zhu Yihai?

00:07:12.959 --> 00:07:14.800
The transfer rights to Aimin Street

00:07:15.079 --> 00:07:16.800
were never yours to begin with

00:07:18.040 --> 00:07:18.759
He should go to Director Ge

00:07:18.759 --> 00:07:19.800
Wouldn't that be more direct?

00:07:22.399 --> 00:07:23.199
Damn it

00:07:23.439 --> 00:07:24.920
We forgot all about Director Ge

00:07:26.879 --> 00:07:27.680
You wait here

00:07:28.279 --> 00:07:29.079
Don't freeze

00:07:29.120 --> 00:07:30.360
Wait for me, I'll be right back

00:07:34.279 --> 00:07:35.560
Who is it? I'm busy

00:07:41.920 --> 00:07:43.759
Director Ge won't give you Aimin Street.

00:07:43.759 --> 00:07:45.240
Think again

00:07:45.480 --> 00:07:48.600
Is Ge Bing at the hospital with Weiwei,

00:07:52.600 --> 00:07:54.879
or at the warehouse with Qiao Lili?

00:07:59.800 --> 00:08:00.480
No

00:08:01.600 --> 00:08:02.720
They're not at either place.

00:08:09.360 --> 00:08:10.920
Enough, enough, Zhu Yihai

00:08:10.920 --> 00:08:11.759
Stop messing around

00:08:13.399 --> 00:08:15.360
Alright, Yihai.

00:08:16.079 --> 00:08:18.480
Let's head to the private room for a proper chat

00:08:21.160 --> 00:08:23.560
How did Yihai get caught?

00:08:25.360 --> 00:08:26.439
What the hell do we do now?

00:08:45.399 --> 00:08:46.919
Zhu Yihai, oh Zhu Yihai

00:08:47.720 --> 00:08:49.679
Do you know why you lost?

00:08:50.799 --> 00:08:51.759
Loser takes the fall.

00:08:52.320 --> 00:08:53.679
Spit it out.

00:08:58.399 --> 00:08:59.240
In a little while,

00:08:59.919 --> 00:09:01.320
my good news will arrive.

00:09:01.879 --> 00:09:03.000
But before that,

00:09:03.720 --> 00:09:05.320
I'll let you die knowing the truth.

00:09:06.679 --> 00:09:07.519
You know what?

00:09:07.879 --> 00:09:08.799
In a few years,

00:09:09.639 --> 00:09:12.720
Aimin Street will be Yecheng's busiest.

00:09:13.200 --> 00:09:15.480
To snatch this prime piece

00:09:15.480 --> 00:09:16.519
from that old fox Ge Zhendong,

00:09:16.519 --> 00:09:17.879
I went through quite some trouble.

00:09:19.080 --> 00:09:19.879
Of course,

00:09:20.039 --> 00:09:21.159
this Guohong Factory

00:09:21.559 --> 00:09:23.039
has a pretty big name in the city too.

00:09:23.519 --> 00:09:24.840
So you needed a hired gun.

00:09:25.240 --> 00:09:26.039
Exactly.

00:09:27.360 --> 00:09:31.679
Zhu Yihai, you have a big rep at Guohong.

00:09:32.200 --> 00:09:34.759
If you helped me deal with Ge Zhendong,

00:09:35.360 --> 00:09:36.600
he'd definitely be in for a rough time.

00:09:37.720 --> 00:09:41.120
Then I'd just need to fan the flames,

00:09:42.240 --> 00:09:43.639
and the deal would be done, wouldn't it?

00:09:45.080 --> 00:09:46.360
How'd you know I'd help you?

00:09:46.519 --> 00:09:48.879
Because you, Zhu Yihai, your whole life

00:09:48.879 --> 00:09:50.919
you've been chasing that "honor" in your heart.

00:09:51.600 --> 00:09:53.279
As long as I played you up,

00:09:54.039 --> 00:09:57.120
you think you could've stayed out of it?

00:09:57.759 --> 00:09:59.200
So nobody was actually after you.

00:09:59.720 --> 00:10:00.759
Of course.

00:10:01.240 --> 00:10:04.559
Who in Yecheng would dare touch Long Xiao?

00:10:07.039 --> 00:10:08.600
I'll be straight with you today.

00:10:09.120 --> 00:10:10.480
My men told me before

00:10:11.039 --> 00:10:11.679
that back then,

00:10:12.240 --> 00:10:14.120
he was the one who raped Qiao Lili.

00:10:14.879 --> 00:10:16.960
So I just went with the flow,

00:10:17.759 --> 00:10:19.759
pretended I was about to be killed,

00:10:19.759 --> 00:10:22.360
and then told you where he was.

00:10:23.399 --> 00:10:24.759
Tell me, would you, Zhu Yihai,

00:10:24.759 --> 00:10:26.720
ever fail to come save your Qiao Lili?

00:10:27.960 --> 00:10:29.240
Once Zhu Yihai finished him off,

00:10:29.240 --> 00:10:30.320
you'd just take advantage of the situation.

00:10:30.440 --> 00:10:31.840
You'd say I saved you,

00:10:32.080 --> 00:10:34.039
make me the number two of Jumu Group.

00:10:34.159 --> 00:10:35.559
Zhu Yihai cares about face,

00:10:36.120 --> 00:10:37.399
so he'd definitely help you.

00:10:37.600 --> 00:10:38.200
Right?

00:10:38.480 --> 00:10:40.039
You're only figuring it out now?

00:10:41.120 --> 00:10:42.159
Too late!

00:10:47.960 --> 00:10:48.720
All right, all right, all right.

00:10:48.840 --> 00:10:49.639
Don't worry.

00:10:50.279 --> 00:10:51.320
After this is all done,

00:10:51.320 --> 00:10:53.320
I'll definitely bury the two of you

00:10:53.799 --> 00:10:54.879
together.

00:11:02.679 --> 00:11:04.240
My good news has arrived.